1. *Visi* mi majica na ramenu. (My shirt *is hanging* off my shoulder.)
2. Na drvetu *visi* crvena jabuka. (A red apple *is hanging* on the tree.)
3. Čekam da se veš *visi*. (I'm waiting for the laundry *to hang* up.)
4. Moram da *visim* novi zavese. (I have to *hang* up new curtains.)
5. *Visi* li slika ravno? (Is the picture *hanging* straight?)
6. Nemoj da *visiš* na internetu celu noć. (Don't *hang* on the internet all night.)
7. Ona uvek *visi* s drugaricama u parku. (She always *hangs out* with her friends in the park.)
8. U kancelariji *visi* tablica sa rasporedom. (There's a schedule board *hanging* in the office.)